{"tid":316164,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】周柏豪加盟星夢娛樂","createTime":"2017-07-10T13:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T13:55:03.000Z","uid":21779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b34c8c31369b1e2ef31ed68127a6e7f1a5f00a","tid":316164,"uid":21779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"09年喺大台《超級巨聲》出道嘅許廷鏗，早前告別大台，轉投華納，６月首次以華納歌手出活動，大台有到場，但冇派人訪問舊將。（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tzd4m1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tzd4m1&d=xrBEIkkbOI%2BdwT7Vu8BMYTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5a743627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tzd4m1</a> ）而原本係華納一哥嘅周柏豪，就喺6月底同結束10年合作關係，將一哥之位讓俾許廷鏗。（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uIekSn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uIekSn&d=xrBEIkkbOI%2BdwT7Vu8BMYTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5e589830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uIekSn</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n柏豪當日活動上話冇造人計劃，仲已經搵到新合作。今日大台代柏豪公佈新消息，原來柏豪聽日會喺香港麗思卡爾頓酒店開新聞發佈會，宣佈加入星夢娛樂&hellip;&hellip;即係填補番許廷鏗個一哥位置。<br />\n至於周柏豪今日就去咗銅鑼灣為代言健身中心做店長，仲話做代言人慳咗唔少錢。問佢慳錢係咪想買「磚頭」？柏豪坦言入市要睇定，因為樓價跌完已回升。<br />\n上年同老婆拉埋天窗，問到柏豪將來置業，會唔會寫老婆名？佢話：「結咗婚寫佢名都名正言順啦！」問佢係咪將財產都交由老婆管？佢好大反應：「我嘅就係我嘅，佢嘅係佢，但佢o依家冇嘢做，就幫我打理生意，我都有責任嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170710/large/1499693150_a535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170710%2Flarge%2F1499693150_a535.jpg&h=0ed41147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好失望，乜咁睇唔開</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"10936385c0da08806a7eb80ea2f2f6a3f7c3d606","tid":316164,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}